rew Serwer - Fortune Brainstorm TECH 2011.jpg|[[Andrew Serwer]]\nFile:Nate Silver 2009.png|[[Nate Silver]]\nFile:Ben Smith journalist (cropped).jpg|[[Ben Smith (journalist)|Ben Smith]]\nFile:Harry Smith.jpg|[[Harry Smith (American journalist)|Harry Smith]]\nFile:Shepard Smith in Studio B crop.jpg|[[Shepard Smith]]\nFile:LaraSpencerAAFeb09.jpg|[[Lara Spencer]]\nFile:Hari_Sreenivasan.jpg|[[Hari Sreenivasan]]\nFile:Lesley Stahl.jpg|[[Lesley Stahl]]\nFile:Brian Stelter @ SXSW 2019 (47300407302) (cropped).jpg|[[Brian Stelter]]\nFile:George Stephanopoulos April 2009.jpg|[[George Stephanopoulos]]\nFile:Jon Stewart MFF 2016.jpg|[[Jon Stewart]]\nFile:Lori stokes 5070478.jpg|[[Lori Stokes]]\nFile:Michael Strahan superbowl parade.jpg|[[Michael Strahan]]\nFile:Interview Arthur Gregg Sulzberger and Michel Temer - Davos - 24012018- crop.jpg|[[A.G. Sulzberger]]\nFile:Arthur Sulzberger Jr.jpg|[[Arthur Ochs Sulzberger Jr.]]\nFile:Mark Thompson, Nytimes @ SXSW 2016.jpg|[[Mark Thompson (media executive)|Mark Thompson]]\nFile:Andy Towle on the Great South Bay of Long Island.jpg|[[Andy Towle]]\nFile:Tur at SXSW 2017 (32703089504) (cropped).jpg|[[Katy Tur]]\nFile:Meredith Vieira (cropped).jpg|[[Meredith Vieira]]\nFile:Barbara Walters 2011.jpg|[[Barbara Walters]]\nFile:Jesse Watters by Gage Skidmore.jpg|[[Jesse Watters]]\nFile:Brian Williams 2011 Shankbone.JPG|[[Brian Williams]]\nFile:Juan williams 2011.jpg|[[Juan Williams]]\nFile:Jenna Wolfe chatting with people (cropped).jpg|[[Jenna Wolfe]]\nFile:Lozupone Jeffyang.png|[[Jeff Yang]]\nFile:RohitVyas.jpg|[[Rohit Vyas]]\nFile:Fareed Zakaria, Peabody Awards (2012) (cropped).jpg|[[Fareed Zakaria]]\n</gallery>\n|caption=New Yorkers in journalism\n}}\n\n===A===\n* [[Roz Abrams]] &ndash; multiple [[broadcast network]]s\n* Ai Heping \u2013 ''[[China Daily]]''<ref name=ChineseBuyers>[http://usa.chinadaily.com.cn/us/2015-10/06/content_22112389.htm] Accessed October 6, 2015.</ref>\n* [[Cristina Alesci]] &ndash; ''[[CNN]]''\n* [[Yashar Ali]] &ndash; 