ws\n* [[Jann Wenner]] \u2013 co-founder and publisher, [[Rolling Stone]]\n* [[Bill Whitaker (journalist)|Bill Whitaker]] &ndash; ''CBS/60 Minutes''\n* [[Brian Williams]] &ndash; NBC News\n* [[Juan Williams]] &ndash; Fox News\n* [[Jenna Wolfe]] \u2013 journalist and TV news host\n* Andrea Wong \u2013 ''Bloomberg News''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://muckrack.com/andreawong|title=Andrea Wong \u2013 Verified|publisher=Muck Rack|accessdate=August 24, 2015}}</ref>\n\n===Y===\n* [[Jeff Yang]] \u2013 \"Tao Jones\" columnist for ''The Wall Street Journal''\n* Lucy Yang \u2013 WABC-TV<ref>[https://abc7ny.com/about/newsteam/lucy-yang/] Accessed February 12, 2019.</ref>\n* Lucy Yang (separate) \u2013 ''[[Insider Inc.|INSIDER]]''{{cn|date=February 2020}}\n* Vivian Yee \u2013 ''The New York Times''<ref>{{cite web|url=http://muckrack.com/vivianhyee|title=Vivian Yee|accessdate=February 23, 2015}}</ref>\n* Claudia Yeung \u2013 communications director, [[Hong Kong Economic and Trade Office]], New York<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hketony.gov.hk/ny/key_personnel.htm|title=Key Personnel|publisher=[[Government of Hong Kong Special Administrative Region]]|date=April 14, 2015|accessdate=May 13, 2015}}</ref>\n* William Yu \u2013 [[digital media]] strategist<ref>[https://www.linkedin.com/in/itswillyu] Accessed May 16, 2016.</ref><ref>[https://www.nytimes.com/2016/05/11/movies/john-cho-starring-in-every-movie-ever-made-a-diversity-hashtag-is-born.html?version=meter+at+4&contentId=&mediaId=&referrer=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F&priority=true&action=click&contentCollection=Technology&module=RelatedCoverage&region=EndOfArticle&pgtype=article] Accessed May 16, 2016.</ref>\n* Jada Yuan \u2013 travel correspondent, ''The New York Times''<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2018/01/10/travel/jada-yuan-52-places-traveler.html|title=Introducing Our 52 Places Traveler|newspaper=The New York Times|date=January 10, 2018|accessdate=February 14, 2018}}</ref>\n* Yun Li \u2013 CNBC<ref>[https://www.