Manhattan]].\n\n{{Compact ToC|pre1=Notable New Yorkers in journalism|prebreak=yes|seealso=yes|refs=yes|e=|i=|u=|x=}}\n\n==New Yorkers in journalism==\n{{Image frame|width=354|content=\n<gallery mode=packed heights=100 style=\"width:350px; background:#fafafa;font-size:85%; line-height:130%;\">\nFile:john_avlon_pic.jpg|[[John Avlon]]\nFile:Pulitzer2018-dean-baquet-20180530-wp.jpg|[[Dean Baquet]]\nFile:Brooke Baldwin on set in DC.jpg|[[Brooke Baldwin]]\nFile:Josh Barro.jpg|[[Josh Barro]]\nFile:Maria Bartiromo.jpg|[[Maria Bartiromo]]\nFile:Joybeharpic.jpg|[[Joy Behar]]\nFile:John Berman.jpg|[[John Berman]]\nFile:Charles blow 2014.jpg|[[Charles Blow]]\nFile:Kate Bolduan.jpg|[[Kate Bolduan]]\nFile:Keith Boykin 2017.jpg|[[Keith Boykin]]\nFile:Malan breton2.jpg|[[Malan Breton]]\nFile:Tom Brokaw 2015.JPG|[[Tom Brokaw]]\nFile:Mika Brzezinski.jpg|[[Mika Brzezinski]]\nFile:Erin Burnett - small.jpg|[[Erin Burnett]]\nFile:Alysin Camerota at 2016 Democratic National Convention.jpg|[[Alisyn Camerota]]\nFile:Gretchen Carlson (27146117519) (cropped).jpg|[[Gretchen Carlson]]\nFile:Neil Cavuto (cropped).jpg|[[Neil Cavuto]]\nFile:Juju Chang.jpg|[[Juju Chang]]\nFile:Adrian Chen at The Influencers - 2017 (26286566559) (cropped).jpg|[[Adrian Chen]]\nFile:012913hometown13 (8428459302).jpg|[[Liz Cho]]\nFile:ConnieChungByPhilKonstantin.jpg|[[Connie Chung]]\nFile:Stephen Colbert December 2017.jpg|[[Stephen Colbert]]\nFile:Anderson Cooper at Tulane University.jpg|[[Anderson Cooper]]\nFile:Bob Costas.JPG|[[Bob Costas]]\nFile:Katie Couric VF 2012 Shankbone 2.JPG|[[Katie Couric]]\nFile:Cronkitenasa.PNG|[[Walter Cronkite]]\nFile:Chris Cuomo at 2016 Democratic National Convention.jpg|[[Chris Cuomo]]\nFile:SECupp-HS5-2.jpg|[[S.E. Cupp]]\nFile:Ann Curry 2012 Shankbone.JPG|[[Ann Curry]]\nFile:Ted_David_2016.jpg|[[Ted David]]\nFile:John Dickerson in 2009.jpg|[[John Dickerson (journalist)|John Dickerson]]\nFile:Steve Doocy.jpg|[[Steve Doocy]]\nFile:Vladimir Duthiers.jpg|[[Vladimir Duthiers]]\nFile:Mauree